ğŸŒ TripTrek Travel Planner API
TripTrek is a Node.js + Express RESTful API connected to MongoDB Atlas that allows users to create and manage travel itineraries. Users can create multiple trips, add destinations and activities, and keep everything organized in one place.
This API supports full CRUD functionality for trips, destinations, and activities.
ğŸš€ Features
Create, read, update, and delete (CRUD) trips, destinations, and activities
Uses Mongoose for MongoDB schema modeling
Secure user accounts tied to individual trips
Connected to MongoDB Atlas cloud database
Supports CORS for client-side interaction
API structure designed for integration with a future front-end UI

